# KobeOS Release Signing Public Key
# Replace this file with the actual GPG public key before building a release.
#
# Generate with:
#   gpg --batch --gen-key build/gpg-keygen-params.txt
#   gpg --armor --export releases@kobepaytech.com > build/kobeos-release.pub
#
# Sign release artifacts with:
#   gpg --detach-sign --armor --output artifact.AppImage.sig artifact.AppImage
#
# Set KOBEOS_RELEASE_KEY_FINGERPRINT env var to the key fingerprint
# for strict fingerprint checking during verification.
